{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 12,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 323.351,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.158,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.338,
      "end": 5.288,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look, and behold thy seed,",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.468,
      "end": 7.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the seed of thy brethren.",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 7.97,
      "end": 11.128,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and beheld the land of promise;",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.308,
      "end": 13.723,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld multitudes of people,",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 13.903,
      "end": 17.711,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even as it were in number as many as the sand of the sea.",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 18.391,
      "end": 21.038,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld multitudes",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 21.218,
      "end": 23.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "gathered together to battle,",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 23.395,
      "end": 24.742,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "one against the other;",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 24.922,
      "end": 26.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld wars,",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 26.727,
      "end": 28.399,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and rumors of wars,",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 28.579,
      "end": 31.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great slaughters with the sword among my people.",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 32.649,
      "end": 36.782,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld many generations pass away,",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 36.962,
      "end": 40.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the manner of wars and contentions in the land;",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 40.718,
      "end": 42.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld many cities,",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 42.895,
      "end": 45.171,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even that I did not number them.",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 45.851,
      "end": 48.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I saw a mist of darkness",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 49.142,
      "end": 51.603,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "on the face of the land of promise;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 51.783,
      "end": 53.362,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw lightnings,",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 53.542,
      "end": 58.047,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I heard thunderings, and earthquakes, and all manner of tumultuous noises;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 58.227,
      "end": 61.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the earth and the rocks, that they rent;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 61.472,
      "end": 64.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw mountains tumbling into pieces;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 64.531,
      "end": 66.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the plains of the earth,",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 67.172,
      "end": 68.751,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they were broken up;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 68.931,
      "end": 71.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many cities that they were sunk;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 72.037,
      "end": 75.148,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many that they were burned with fire;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 75.328,
      "end": 78.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many that did tumble to the earth,",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 78.341,
      "end": 80.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the quaking thereof.",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 80.832,
      "end": 83.897,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after I saw these things,",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 84.077,
      "end": 86.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw the vapor of darkness,",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 86.44,
      "end": 88.948,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it passed from off the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 89.128,
      "end": 92.332,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold, I saw multitudes who had not fallen",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 92.512,
      "end": 96.274,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the great and terrible judgments of the Lord.",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 96.954,
      "end": 98.765,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw the heavens open,",
      "verse": "12:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 98.945,
      "end": 101.824,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lamb of God descending out of heaven;",
      "verse": "12:6",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 102.004,
      "end": 104.558,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he came down and showed himself unto them.",
      "verse": "12:6",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 105.238,
      "end": 107.328,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also saw and bear record",
      "verse": "12:7",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 107.508,
      "end": 110.573,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Holy Ghost fell upon twelve others;",
      "verse": "12:7",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 110.753,
      "end": 113.354,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were ordained of God, and chosen.",
      "verse": "12:7",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 114.034,
      "end": 116.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "12:8",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 116.397,
      "end": 118.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the twelve disciples of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "12:8",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 119.131,
      "end": 121.778,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are chosen to minister unto thy seed.",
      "verse": "12:8",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 122.458,
      "end": 123.991,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said unto me:",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 124.171,
      "end": 126.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou rememberest the twelve apostles of the Lamb?",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 126.952,
      "end": 128.438,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold they are they",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 128.618,
      "end": 131.404,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who shall judge the twelve tribes of Israel;",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 131.584,
      "end": 136.553,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the twelve ministers of thy seed shall be judged of them;",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 136.733,
      "end": 139.055,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for ye are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 139.735,
      "end": 143.822,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And these twelve ministers whom thou beholdest shall judge thy seed.",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 144.002,
      "end": 146.417,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And, behold, they are righteous forever;",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 146.597,
      "end": 149.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for because of their faith in the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 149.61,
      "end": 152.118,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their garments are made white in his blood.",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 152.798,
      "end": 154.609,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 154.789,
      "end": 155.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 155.805,
      "end": 160.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked, and beheld three generations pass away in righteousness;",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 160.397,
      "end": 162.394,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their garments were white",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 162.574,
      "end": 164.803,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even like unto the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 164.983,
      "end": 166.794,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 166.974,
      "end": 169.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These are made white in the blood of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 169.801,
      "end": 172.03,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their faith in him.",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 172.71,
      "end": 176.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, also saw many of the fourth generation",
      "verse": "12:12",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 176.327,
      "end": 178.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who passed away in righteousness.",
      "verse": "12:12",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 179.329,
      "end": 183.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I saw the multitudes of the earth gathered together.",
      "verse": "12:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 184.56,
      "end": 186.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "12:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 186.551,
      "end": 189.848,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold thy seed, and also the seed of thy brethren.",
      "verse": "12:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 190.528,
      "end": 192.804,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I looked",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 192.984,
      "end": 195.399,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and beheld the people of my seed",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 195.579,
      "end": 197.901,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "gathered together in multitudes",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 198.081,
      "end": 200.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "against the seed of my brethren;",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 200.49,
      "end": 202.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were gathered together to battle.",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 203.446,
      "end": 205.629,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 205.809,
      "end": 209.431,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the fountain of filthy water which thy father saw;",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 209.611,
      "end": 212.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even the river of which he spake;",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 212.485,
      "end": 215.968,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the depths thereof are the depths of hell.",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 216.648,
      "end": 218.691,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the mists of darkness",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 218.871,
      "end": 221.054,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are the temptations of the devil,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 221.234,
      "end": 222.859,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which blindeth the eyes,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 223.039,
      "end": 225.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hardeneth the hearts of the children of men,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 226.052,
      "end": 228.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and leadeth them away into broad roads,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 228.879,
      "end": 231.155,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they perish and are lost.",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 231.835,
      "end": 234.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the large and spacious building,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 234.43,
      "end": 237.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which thy father saw, is vain imaginations",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 237.489,
      "end": 239.672,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the pride of the children of men.",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 239.852,
      "end": 243.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And a great and a terrible gulf divideth them;",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 243.236,
      "end": 246.812,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even the word of the justice of the Eternal God,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 246.992,
      "end": 249.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Messiah who is the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 249.726,
      "end": 252.605,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of whom the Holy Ghost beareth record,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 252.785,
      "end": 256.593,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the beginning of the world until this time,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 256.773,
      "end": 259.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and from this time henceforth and forever.",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 260.1,
      "end": 262.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And while the angel spake these words,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 262.695,
      "end": 264.274,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I beheld and saw",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 264.454,
      "end": 268.03,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the seed of my brethren did contend against my seed,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 268.21,
      "end": 270.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the word of the angel;",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 270.851,
      "end": 273.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and because of the pride of my seed,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 273.353,
      "end": 275.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the temptations of the devil,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 275.53,
      "end": 280.406,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I beheld that the seed of my brethren did overpower the people of my seed.",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 281.086,
      "end": 283.362,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld,",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 283.542,
      "end": 286.653,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and saw the people of the seed of my brethren",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 286.833,
      "end": 288.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they had overcome my seed;",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 289.149,
      "end": 292.632,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they went forth in multitudes upon the face of the land.",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 293.312,
      "end": 296.702,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw them gathered together in multitudes;",
      "verse": "12:21",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 296.882,
      "end": 300.133,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw wars and rumors of wars among them;",
      "verse": "12:21",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 300.313,
      "end": 304.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in wars and rumors of wars I saw many generations pass away.",
      "verse": "12:21",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 305.265,
      "end": 307.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "12:22",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 307.256,
      "end": 309.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold these shall dwindle in unbelief.",
      "verse": "12:22",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 310.351,
      "end": 312.627,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld,",
      "verse": "12:23",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 312.807,
      "end": 315.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after they had dwindled in unbelief",
      "verse": "12:23",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 315.309,
      "end": 318.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they became a dark, and loathsome, and a filthy people,",
      "verse": "12:23",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 319.065,
      "end": 322.687,
      "type": "line",
